fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">f. </div><div class="t m352 x4d h3d y21d ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I will not tolerate a proud or arrogant person, v. 5. </div><div class="t m565 xb h3d y8a1 ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">g. </div><div class="t m343 xa7 h3d y8a2 ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I will approve the faithful and let them live in my palace, v. 6. </div><div class="t m299 xb h3d y8a3 ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">h. </div><div class="t m96 x4d h3d y8a3 ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">No liar will live in my palace, v. 7. </div><div class="t m566 xb h3d y8a4 ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">i. </div><div class="t m567 x4d h3d y487 ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">No hypocrite will remain in my presence, v. 7. </div><div class="t m341 xb h3d y8a5 ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">j. </div><div class="t m332 xa7 h3d y220 ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I will expel evil from the city of the Lord, v. 8. </div><div class="t m10b xf h3c y8a6 ff1 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">16. Evaluate how well David lived up to his own charter. </div><div class="t m568 xf h3c y8a7 ff1 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">68 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
